blitzmax-geany-plugin
=====================

Geany plugin which adds some blitzmax flavor



Build on Linux
--------------

1. cd into the plugin dir
2. "./autogen.sh"
3. "cd blitzmax"
4. "sudo make install"

6. restart Geany
7. "tools" -> "plugin manager"
7.1 [x] BlitzMax-Addon
7.2 click on "Preferences"
7.3 enter the BlitzMax-path
7.4 click "Ok"

Finish.
